metadata.name: Ticket to the Toy Factory
metadata.description:
Ticket to the Toy Factory is your key to enter the Mean Toys Universe. 
 
 Mean Toys Universe will provide you both digital collectible and physical figure toy that is customized to your pfp. 
 
 1 ticket is equal to 1 Mean Toy Claim. 
 
 For every 3 tickets, you are eligible to claim a Lego Technic Inspired Mean Toy of your choice.
